n=5: 1024 tournaments, 9 score classes

Betti vector distribution:
  [np.int64(1), np.int64(0), np.int64(0), np.int64(0), np.int64(0)]: 720
  [np.int64(1), np.int64(1), np.int64(0), np.int64(0), np.int64(0)]: 304

beta_1 = 1 vs H-max within score class:
  Score (np.int64(1), np.int64(1), np.int64(2), np.int64(3), np.int64(3)): max_H=9, beta_1=1 H=[9], beta_1=0 H=[9], max in b1? True
  Score (np.int64(1), np.int64(2), np.int64(2), np.int64(2), np.int64(3)): max_H=15, beta_1=1 H=[11, 15], beta_1=0 H=[13], max in b1? True
